<lb n="0159b04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0159022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><title>穢跡金剛<note n="0159023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法）＋禁【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禁【大】，法禁【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159023"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">法禁</rdg></app>百變<note n="0159024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（門）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，法門【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159024"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">法門</rdg></app><note n="0159025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經一卷〕－【宋】</note><note n="0159025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0159025"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></title><note n="0159026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【元】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0159026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159026"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0159b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0159b06" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0159027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔北天竺國〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">北天竺國【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159027"><lem wit="【大】">北天竺國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三藏沙門阿質
<lb n="0159b07" ed="T"/>達霰<note n="0159028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唐言無能勝將〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唐言無能勝將【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159028"><lem wit="【大】">唐言無能勝將</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0159b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0159b0801">爾時金剛復白佛言。世尊若有善男子善女
<lb n="0159b09" ed="T"/>人。持我此呪無効驗者無有是處。欲令山摧
<lb n="0159b10" ed="T"/>者。取白芥子三升上好安<note n="0159029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝息【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0159029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】＊，息【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0159029"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香。於山中疑有
<lb n="0159b11" ed="T"/><note n="0159030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＋（處）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶【大】，寶處【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159030"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">寶處</rdg></app>。取<note n="0159031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鑌＝賓【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鑌【大】，賓【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159031"><lem wit="【大】">鑌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">賓</rdg></app>鐵刀一枚。畫四方為界。<note n="0159032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耳＝取【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳【大】，取【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159032"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">取</rdg></app>淨巾
<lb n="0159b12" ed="T"/>一枚香爐一枚。燒安<app type="star" corresp="#0159029"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香先呪一千八遍。取
<lb n="0159b13" ed="T"/>白芥子四散<note n="0159033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及＝乃【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，乃【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159033"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">乃</rdg></app>至七遍。作是法其山自摧。若
<lb n="0159b14" ed="T"/>有寶之處其藏神捨寶而出任意用之。若欲
<lb n="0159b15" ed="T"/>令海竭者。先呪一千八遍。以金銅作一龍形。
<lb n="0159b16" ed="T"/>擲於海中即時海竭。若欲令江河逆流者。取
<lb n="0159b17" ed="T"/>安<app type="star" corresp="#0159029"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香作一象形。無問大小擲水中呪一百
<lb n="0159b18" ed="T"/>八遍。<note n="0159034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登＝即ィ【甲】</note><note n="0159034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">登【大】，即【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159034"><lem wit="【大】">登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">即</rdg></app>時逆流。令依舊者呪一淨石擲之
<lb n="0159b19" ed="T"/>水中其水如故。若有雷電霹靂毒龍卒風惡
<lb n="0159b20" ed="T"/>雨者。即作止雷<note n="0159035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">電＝雹【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">電【大】，雹【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159035"><lem wit="【大】">電</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">雹</rdg></app>印。以左手中指無名指
<lb n="0159b21" ed="T"/>小指並屈掌中。<note n="0159036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（直）ィ＋頭【甲】</note><note n="0159036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭【大】，直頭【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159036"><lem wit="【大】">頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">直頭</rdg></app>指以大<note n="0159037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">母＝拇【三】【甲】下同</note><note n="0159037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母【大】下同，拇【宋】【元】【明】【甲】下同</note><app n="0159037"><lem wit="【大】">母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">拇</rdg></app>指。捻頭指中
<lb n="0159b22" ed="T"/>節上。誦呪呪之。以印遙指雷雹之處自止。
<lb n="0159b23" ed="T"/>若欲令一切鬼神自來歸伏為給使者。取水
<lb n="0159b24" ed="T"/>三<note n="0159038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">斗＝升【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗【大】，升【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159038"><lem wit="【大】">斗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">升</rdg></app>盛銅器中。以淨灰圍之。即作<note n="0159039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝都【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教【大】，都【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159039"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">都</rdg></app>攝錄
<lb n="0159b25" ed="T"/>印。以二無名指並屈掌中。令背相倚。二中
<lb n="0159b26" ed="T"/>指頭相捻。二頭指及小指各如開華。以大母
<lb n="0159b27" ed="T"/>指<note n="0159040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捻＋（頭指）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捻【大】，捻頭指【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159040"><lem wit="【大】">捻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">捻頭指</rdg></app>中節。默呪一百八遍。其世界內所有
<lb n="0159b28" ed="T"/>諸惡鬼。並來雲集自現其身。捨毒惡心任行
<lb n="0159b29" ed="T"/>人驅<note n="0159041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">使＋（若有百鳥與人作怪者即向鳥作怪之處誦明一百八遍其鳥自來而死）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0159041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">使【大】，使若有百鳥與人作怪者即向鳥作怪之處誦明一百八遍其鳥自來而死【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159041"><lem wit="【大】">使</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">使若有百鳥與人作怪者即向鳥作怪之處誦明一百八遍其鳥自來而死</rdg></app>。若禁山者所至之山。誦呪百遍大
<pb n="0159c" xml:id="T21.1229.0159c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0159c01" ed="T"/>叫三聲。即作<note n="0159042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔業山〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">業山【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159042"><lem wit="【大】">業山</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>印以<note n="0159043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左ィ【甲】</note><note n="0159043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，左【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159043"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">左</rdg></app>手無名<note n="0159044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＋（小指）【甲】</note><note n="0159044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">指【大】，指小指【甲】</note><app n="0159044"><lem wit="【大】">指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">指小指</rdg></app>。屈
<lb n="0159c02" ed="T"/>於掌中。直竪中頭大<note n="0159045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">母等指＝拇指等【甲】</note><note n="0159045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母等指【大】，拇指等【甲】</note><app n="0159045"><lem wit="【大】">母等指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拇指等</rdg></app>。並直竪。向<note n="0159046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝山【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，山【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159046"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">山</rdg></app>
<lb n="0159c03" ed="T"/>印之七遍。即却行七步。<note n="0159047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝復ィ【甲】</note><note n="0159047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，復【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159047"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">復</rdg></app>七<note n="0159048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即【三】</note><note n="0159048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，即【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159048"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">即</rdg></app>山。<note n="0159049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其山中〕ィ－【甲】</note><note n="0159049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其山中【大】，〔－〕【校異-甲】</note><app n="0159049"><lem wit="【大】">其
<lb n="0159c04" ed="T"/>山中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>即一切鳥<note n="0159050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狩【大】，獸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159050"><lem wit="【大】">狩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">獸</rdg></app>並移出山。若作此印呪七
<lb n="0159c05" ed="T"/>遍。以印向空中印三七度。其空中毫塵不
<lb n="0159c06" ed="T"/><note n="0159051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">過＝遇【三】</note><note n="0159051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過【大】，遇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159051"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遇</rdg></app>。若欲令人不語者。<note n="0159052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＝畫【三】</note><note n="0159052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書【大】，畫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159052"><lem wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">畫</rdg></app>前人姓名。向口
<lb n="0159c07" ed="T"/>中含<note n="0159053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">口＝之【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">口【大】，之【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159053"><lem wit="【大】">口</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">之</rdg></app>。其人口不<note n="0159054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能＝離【宋】【元】</note><note n="0159054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">能【大】，離【宋】【元】</note><app n="0159054"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">離</rdg></app>言。吐出即語得。若誦
<lb n="0159c08" ed="T"/>一切諸呪先須作壇。若誦我此呪者即勿須
<lb n="0159c09" ed="T"/>作壇。但剋一跋枳金剛<note n="0159055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">榼＝猛【甲】</note><note n="0159055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">榼【大】，猛【甲】</note><app n="0159055"><lem wit="【大】">榼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">猛</rdg></app>杵。於佛塔中或
<lb n="0159c10" ed="T"/>於靜室中。用香泥塗地隨其大小。著種種香
<lb n="0159c11" ed="T"/>華供養。安杵壇中呪一百八遍。其杵即自動。
<lb n="0159c12" ed="T"/>或變作種種異物亦勿怪之。更誦呪一百八
<lb n="0159c13" ed="T"/>遍。其杵自去地三尺以來。或五六七尺乃至
<lb n="0159c14" ed="T"/>一丈以來。持法之人即須歸依懺悔發願。我
<lb n="0159c15" ed="T"/>於彼中即現真身。隨行人意所願樂者。並皆
<lb n="0159c16" ed="T"/>速得如意。我即與授菩提之記。即得身心解
<lb n="0159c17" ed="T"/>脫。先須誦十萬遍滿。然後作法若課未充不
<lb n="0159c18" ed="T"/>得効驗。</p>
<pb n="0160a" xml:id="T21.1229.0160a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a01" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><head>印法第二</head>
<lb n="0160a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a0201"><note n="0160001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麗本印圖總無之今依明本載之</note>印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_01.gif"/></figure>此印方一寸八分<note n="0160002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">刻＝剋【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0160002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">刻【大】＊，剋【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0160002"><lem wit="【大】">刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。呪
<lb n="0160a03" ed="T"/>一千遍。<note n="0160003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＝用【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，用【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160003"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">用</rdg></app>白膠香度之。剋
<lb n="0160a04" ed="T"/>印日勿令人見。用印印心。得
<lb n="0160a05" ed="T"/>心智自然智宿命智。持印百
<lb n="0160a06" ed="T"/>日。即<note n="0160004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得住＝任得【甲】</note><note n="0160004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得住【大】，任得【甲】</note><app n="0160004"><lem wit="【大】">得<note n="0160005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝任【三】</note><note n="0160005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住【大】，任【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0160005"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">任</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">任得</rdg></app>種種大法<note n="0160006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（也）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門【大】，門也【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160006"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">門也</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0160a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a0701">印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_02.gif"/></figure>方一寸二分呪六百遍。以安
<lb n="0160a08" ed="T"/><note n="0160007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝息【明】【甲】</note><note n="0160007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】，息【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160007"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香度之。帶行令一切人愛
<lb n="0160a09" ed="T"/>樂<note n="0160008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔得〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160008"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大自在永離眾苦。</p>
<lb n="0160a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a1001">印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_03.gif"/></figure>方一寸五分<app type="star" corresp="#0160002"><lem wit="【大】">刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。呪六百
<lb n="0160a11" ed="T"/>遍。以白膠香度之。用印印
<lb n="0160a12" ed="T"/>脚。便得飛騰<note n="0160009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔虛〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虛【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160009"><lem wit="【大】">虛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>空所向自
<lb n="0160a13" ed="T"/>在。</p>
<lb n="0160a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a1401">印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_04.gif"/></figure>方一寸八分<app type="star" corresp="#0160002"><lem wit="【大】">刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。用白膠香
<lb n="0160a15" ed="T"/>度之。呪七千遍。用印印足。可
<lb n="0160a16" ed="T"/>日行三百萬里無人得見。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0160a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><head><note n="0160010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神變延命法五字麗本無之今依明本補載之</note>神變延命法</head>
<lb n="0160a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a2001">印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_05.gif"/></figure>伏連。書心上即差。大吉急急
<lb n="0160a21" ed="T"/>如律令。</p>
<lb n="0160a22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a2301">印<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_06.gif"/></figure>心<note n="0160011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">痛＝為【三】【甲】，病ヵ【甲】</note><note n="0160011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痛【大】，為【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，病【考偽-甲】</note><app n="0160011"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">痛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">病</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">為</rdg></app>。書之立即除差。大吉
<lb n="0160a24" ed="T"/>利急急如律令先呪七遍。</p>
<lb n="0160a25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160a2701"><note n="0160012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下至印法終麗本無之今依明本補載之</note><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_07.gif"/></figure>鬼病。朱書吞之。<figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_08.gif"/></figure>精魅鬼病之人。朱吞之七大書枚立瘥神驗。</p>
<lb n="0160a28" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a29" ed="T"/>
<pb n="0160b" xml:id="T21.1229.0160b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b0101"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_09.gif"/></figure>若<note n="0160013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依＝作【宋】</note><note n="0160013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">依【大】，作【宋】</note><app n="0160013"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">作</rdg></app>法之人。取白檀綾二
<lb n="0160b02" ed="T"/>丈一尺七寸。白練裹之。置
<lb n="0160b03" ed="T"/>於地輪世界。令人延年得
<lb n="0160b04" ed="T"/>七十歲。若無人送者。即安
<lb n="0160b05" ed="T"/>自宅中庭。掘地七尺埋之
<lb n="0160b06" ed="T"/>亦得。又得聰明多智辯才
<lb n="0160b07" ed="T"/>無礙。</p>
<lb n="0160b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b0801">
<lb n="0160b09" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_10.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_11.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_12.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b1101">
<lb n="0160b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b13" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_13.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_14.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_15.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b1601"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_16.gif"/></figure>此七道亦能治萬病。吞之亦
<lb n="0160b17" ed="T"/>令人長壽益智大神驗。</p>
<lb n="0160b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b1801">
<lb n="0160b19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b20" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_17.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_18.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_19.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b2201">
<lb n="0160b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b24" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_20.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_21.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_22.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160b25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160b2701"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_23.gif"/></figure>此上七道用朱書紙上。吞之
<lb n="0160b28" ed="T"/>千枚令人延年。即得與天地
<lb n="0160b29" ed="T"/>齊壽。不得令人見之。</p>
<pb n="0160c" xml:id="T21.1229.0160c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c0101">
<lb n="0160c02" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_24.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_25.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_26.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160c03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c0401">
<lb n="0160c05" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_27.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_28.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_29.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c0701"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_30.gif"/></figure>此上七道若有人患一切病。
<lb n="0160c08" ed="T"/>以此符書之皆得除瘥。若人
<lb n="0160c09" ed="T"/>書符吞之者。延年益智大驗
<lb n="0160c10" ed="T"/>効矣。</p>
<lb n="0160c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c1101">
<lb n="0160c12" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_31.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_32.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_33.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c1401">
<lb n="0160c15" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_34.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_35.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_36.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160c16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c1701"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_37.gif"/></figure>此上七道若有人求種種珍寶
<lb n="0160c18" ed="T"/>者。以朱書此符吞之滿七日。
<lb n="0160c19" ed="T"/>即有種種妙寶自然而至。若
<lb n="0160c20" ed="T"/>求他人財物。當書彼人姓名
<lb n="0160c21" ed="T"/>於符下。其人立即送物到。</p>
<lb n="0160c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c2201">
<lb n="0160c23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c24" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_38.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_39.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0160_40.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0160c25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0160c2701">此上三符朱書床四脚上。常有八大金剛
<lb n="0160c28" ed="T"/>衛護<note n="0160014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝時ヵ【甲】</note><note n="0160014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】，時【考偽-甲】</note><app n="0160014"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">時</rdg></app>不暫捨。惟須嚴淨勿令污染之物
<lb n="0160c29" ed="T"/>入房。切須慎之。</p>
<pb n="0161a" xml:id="T21.1229.0161a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a0101"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_01.gif"/></figure>有大火災起者。書符擲一枚
<lb n="0161a02" ed="T"/>呪一百八遍。向火中須臾災
<lb n="0161a03" ed="T"/>自滅。</p>
<lb n="0161a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a0501"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_02.gif"/></figure><note n="0161001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝大【元】</note><note n="0161001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">火【大】，大【元】</note><app n="0161001"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">大</rdg></app>惡風起者。書此符呪一
<lb n="0161a06" ed="T"/>百八遍。擲向風中即止。</p>
<lb n="0161a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a0801"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_03.gif"/></figure>有大水起者。書此符擲於水
<lb n="0161a09" ed="T"/>中。立即斷流水不溺人矣。</p>
<lb n="0161a10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a1101"><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_04.gif"/></figure>有大雨者。書此符呪之一百
<lb n="0161a12" ed="T"/>八遍。向雨擲之其雨立即自
<lb n="0161a13" ed="T"/>定之。</p>
<lb n="0161a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a1401">
<lb n="0161a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a16" ed="T"/><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_05.gif"/></figure><figure><graphic url="../figures/T/T21p0161_06.gif"/></figure></p>
<lb n="0161a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a1901">此符朱書吞三枚。<note n="0161002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及＝乃ヵ【甲】</note><note n="0161002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，乃【考偽-甲】</note><app n="0161002"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">乃</rdg></app>可與他人書符。
<lb n="0161a20" ed="T"/>即有驗効。若不爾者用諸符無驗。</p>
<lb n="0161a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161a2101">爾時穢跡金剛說此符已。大眾同聲讚言。善
<lb n="0161a22" ed="T"/>哉大力士汝能說是大妙之法。令諸眾生皆
<lb n="0161a23" ed="T"/>得解脫。爾時金剛頃白諸大眾。當知我於汝
<lb n="0161a24" ed="T"/>等。此法若流行之處。我等大<note n="0161003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝夭【宋】【元】</note><note n="0161003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，夭【宋】【元】</note><app n="0161003"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">夭</rdg></app>常當護此行
<lb n="0161a25" ed="T"/>法之人助令成就。是時金剛復作是言。若有
<lb n="0161a26" ed="T"/>眾生行此法者。我即往彼現其人前。所求<note n="0161004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">願＝之【宋】【元】</note><note n="0161004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願【大】，之【宋】【元】</note><app n="0161004"><lem wit="【大】">願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0161a27" ed="T"/>者我亦施與。令彼得種種變現種種神通所
<lb n="0161a28" ed="T"/>作無礙。常須念我本師釋迦牟尼佛。我即常
<lb n="0161a29" ed="T"/>隨逐之。令一切法皆助成就。爾時金剛說此
<pb n="0161b" xml:id="T21.1229.0161b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161b01" ed="T"/>法已。大眾倍加悲喜。及諸天龍大鬼神等。各
<lb n="0161b02" ed="T"/>奉聖言禮足而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0161b03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title>穢跡金剛<note n="0161005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法）＋禁【三】</note><note n="0161005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禁【大】，法禁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0161005"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">法禁</rdg></app>百<note n="0161006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">變＋（法門）【明】</note><note n="0161006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">變【大】，變法門【明】</note><app n="0161006"><lem wit="【大】">變</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">變法門</rdg></app>經</title><note n="0161007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】</note><note n="0161007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0161007"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0161b04" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><note n="0161008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔古經…訶〕六行－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0161008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->〔古經…訶〕六行八十一字－【宋】【元】</note><app cb:word-count="81" n="0161008"><lem wit="【大】"><p xml:id="pT21p0161b0401"><note place="inline">古經本呪四十三字。唐太宗朝人多持誦感驗非一。除去十字今就錄出。速獲靈應無過是呪</note>。</p>
<lb n="0161b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161b0501">唵𠲽咶　啒㖀摩訶般囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　很那𠵨　吻汁
<lb n="0161b06" ed="T"/>吻　（醯）（摩）（尼）𡀎咭𡀎　摩那棲（唵）（斫）（急）
<lb n="0161b07" ed="T"/>（那）烏深暮　啒㖀吽吽（吽）泮泮泮（泮）（泮）娑
<lb n="0161b08" ed="T"/>訶</p></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0161b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161b0901"><note place="inline">真覺彈師所傳神呪。與今經呪同。但梵音賖切字語少異</note>。</p>
<lb n="0161b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0161b1001">唵佛㖃窟聿　摩訶般那很那詡　吻泮吻
<lb n="0161b11" ed="T"/>　尾劼尾　摩那棲　烏澁謨　窟聿吽吽吽
<lb n="0161b12" ed="T"/>　發發發　莎訶<note n="0161009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書云貞享四年仲春七夜以和本校之和本無符亦文言大異淨嚴四十九載，元祿十六年正月二十三日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教，寶永五龍次戊子年十一月六日一校了苾芻性寂</note></p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>